== CodeIgniter v2.0.2 with DataMapper ORM for CI
DataMapper v.1.8.2 on top of CodeIgniter v2.0.2's Active Record
An easier way to deal with database.

== Description of Contents

The default directory structure of a generated Ruby on Rails application:

  |--framework
  |  |-- application
  |  |    |-- controllers
  |  |    |-- core
  |  |    |-- helpers
  |  |    |-- libraries
  |  |    |-- models
  |  |    `-- views
  |  |        `-- layouts
  |  `-- system
  |      |-- core
  |      |-- database
  |      |-- helpers
  |      |-- libraries
  |
  |-- public <-- web server document root pointing to this directory
  |   |-- assets
  |   |   `-- css
  |   |   `-- images
  |   |   `-- js
  |   |-- index.php

